quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  105,1,"Tewamanya Katonda kyeyakola eggye ly’enjovu?"
  105,2,"Enkwe zaabwe tezaagwa butaka?"
  105,3,"N'abasindikira e binnyonyi nga bijjira mu bibinja."
  105,4,"Nga bibakanyugira amayinja amookye."
  105,5,"Nebafuuka nga omuddo ogagayiddwa ensolo ne gufuluma nga gufuuse obusa."
